WEBVTT

00:07:29.319 --> 00:07:30.758
across the globe.

00:07:31.346 --> 00:07:32.505
And they, like me,

00:07:32.529 --> 00:07:37.459
go through the emotions
of stigma and exclusion.

00:07:38.602 --> 00:07:42.078
And so I have made it my life journey

00:07:42.102 --> 00:07:44.686
to keep these conversations going,

00:07:44.710 --> 00:07:47.885
and I keep confessing about my affair

00:07:47.909 --> 00:07:51.263
so that those people who do not
have the diagnosis

00:07:51.287 --> 00:07:55.224
might know and might have
a constant reminder

00:07:55.248 --> 00:07:58.428
that it is alright to engage
with people like us,

00:07:58.452 --> 00:08:04.012
that as long as they pull down
the walls of stigma and exclusion,